extends layout.pug

block content
  h1 Help
  p Here you can find help and FAQs.
  h2 Frequently Asked Questions
  ul
    li
      h3 How do I add a task?
      p To add a task, log in and use the form on the home page.
    li
      h3 How do I delete a task?
      p To delete a task, log in and use the delete button next to the task.
  h2 Contact Us
  form(action="/send-message" method="post")
    label(for="name") Name:
    input(type="text" name="name" required)
    label(for="email") Email:
    input(type="email" name="email" required)
    label(for="message") Message:
    textarea(name="message" required)
    button(type="submit") Send Message